2%3A%22These%20Bottles%20Decompose%20in%20180%20Days%20%26amp%3B%20Look%20Like%20They%E2%80%99re%20Made%20of%20Plastic!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFrom%20storing%20water%20to%20juices%20and%20various%20other%20daily%20essentials%2C%20plastic%20containers%20have%20become%20ubiquitous%20in%20our%20surroundings.%20Despite%20India%E2%80%99s%20ban%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F202988%2Fchildrens-day-kids-fighting-climate-change-plastic-air-pollution-delhi-ncr-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esingle-use%20plastic%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewe%20see%20little%20change%20in%20the%20amount%20of%20plastic%20waste%20in%20landfills.%20While%20many%20states%20have%20enforced%20bans%20on%20single-use%20plastic%2C%20plastic%20water%20bottles%20remain%20a%20common%20source%20of%20plastic%20waste%20ending%20up%20in%20landfills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EMoneycontrol%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CApproximately%202.8%20lakh%20tonnes%20of%20plastic%20bottle%20waste%20goes%20uncollected%20annually.%20The%20environmental%20impact%20is%20significant.%20Macroplastics%2C%20including%20PET%2C%20often%20clog%20sewage%20systems%20in%20urban%20and%20rural%20areas%2C%20pollute%20rivers%2C%20lakes%2C%20and%20beaches%2C%20and%20degrade%20the%20aesthetic%20and%20ecological%20value%20of%20tourist%20destinations%20and%20landscapes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20combat%20the%20escalating%20issue%20of%20plastic%20waste%2C%20many%20individuals%20and%20changemakers%20have%20devised%20various%20solutions.%20Among%20these%20innovators%20is%20Nikhil%20Kumar%20of%20Greenevon%20Bio%20Bottles%2C%20who%20has%20pioneered%20a%20bottle%20made%20from%20sugarcane!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20bottle%20is%20100%25%20biodegradable%20and%20100%25%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331134%2Fgujarat-sustainable-startup-reroute-makes-ecofriendly-shoes-from-sugarcane-plastic-bottles%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enatural%20made%20using%20sugarcane%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20bottles%20are%20environment%20friendly%20and%20only%20take%20180%20days%20to%20degrade%20when%20exposed%20to%20moisture%20and%20high%20temperatures%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nikhil%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20how%20did%20this%20innovator%20innovate%20a%20bottle%20using%20a%20plant%3F%20We%20were%20as%20intrigued%20as%20you%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98It%20is%20my%20dream%20to%20make%20the%20world%20greener%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Nikhil%20always%20harboured%20a%20passion%20for%20business.%20After%20completing%20his%20graduation%2C%20he%20resolved%20to%20embark%20on%20an%20entrepreneurial%20journey%20of%20his%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20isn%E2%80%99t%20my%20first%20venture%20into%20the%20business%20world.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20always%20been%20driven%20to%20create%20something%20that%E2%80%99s%20uniquely%20mine.%20Initially%2C%20I%20ventured%20into%20the%20coffee%20industry%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20stint%20in%20the%20clothing%20business%2C%20before%20transitioning%20into%20eco-friendly%20ventures%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20of%20us%2C%20Nikhil%20grew%20up%20surrounded%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F316563%2Ftamil-nadu-sustsainable-home-with-plastic-bottles-and-mud-chuzi-vinu-daniel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevalent%20use%20of%20plastic%20bottles.%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20an%20overnight%20realisation%2C%20but%20I%E2%80%99ve%20always%20been%20conscious%20of%20environmental%20issues%20for%20as%20long%20as%20I%20can%20recall.%20However%2C%20when%20it%20came%20to%20taking%20action%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20sense%20of%20purpose%2C%E2%80%9D%20he