%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F293356%2Fhealth-benefits-of-kanji-fermented-rice-water-ancient-south-india-food-science%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecool%2C%20refreshing%20beverage%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20be%20it%20any%20occasion%20%E2%80%94%20after%20a%20delightful%20lunch%2C%20an%20exciting%20evening%20of%20cricket%2C%20or%20a%20quick%20gulp%20after%20a%20shopping%20stroll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBoosting%20retailer%20revenue%20and%20consumer%20experience%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoca-Cola%E2%80%99s%20coolers%20are%20now%20contributing%20to%20increased%20revenues%20for%20retailers%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20micro%2C%20small%2C%20and%20medium%20players%2C%20many%20of%20them%20having%20access%20to%20coolers%20following%20the%20electrification%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20consumers%2C%20the%20benefits%20are%20evident%3A%20Not%20only%20do%20they%20have%20a%20chilled%20beverage%2C%20but%20they%20are%20also%20assured%20of%20its%20purity%20and%20hygiene.%20They%20also%20present%20them%20with%20an%20array%20of%20options%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20diversity%20that%20a%20Coca-Cola%20cooler%2C%20with%20exclusive%20rack%20space%20for%20its%20products%2C%20provides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20retailers%2C%20the%20benefits%20are%20manifold.%20One%2C%20the%20advent%20of%20more%20coolers%2C%20especially%20in%20remote%20areas%2C%20has%20helped%20attract%20new%20consumers%2C%20increasing%20their%20share%20of%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297294%2Fhistory-origin-of-south-india-iconic-drinks-filter-coffee-jigarthanda-tamil-nadu-kerala%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enon-alcoholic%20beverages%3C%2Fa%3E%20market%20is%20growing%20at%20a%20CAGR%20of%208.7%20percent%20to%20INR%201%2C47%2C233%20crores%20by%202030%2C%20and%20by%20product%20categories%2C%20Indians%20consume%20carbonated%20beverages%20the%20most%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20Indian%20Council%20for%20Research%20on%20International%20Economic%20Relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20introduction%20of%20coolers%20has%20given%20many%20retailers%20a%20boost%20%E2%80%94%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20those%20who%20continue%20to%20sell%20them%20either%20stored%20in%20the%20open%20or%20tucked%20into%20ice%20bags.%20It%20is%20not%20just%20the%20optics%20of%20flaunting%20a%20cooler%2C%20it%20is%20the%20purity%20and%20hygiene%20associated%20with%20a%20refrigerated%20cooler%20that%20influences%20consumer%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20retailers%20through%20the%20Superpower%20Retailer%20Program%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnil%20Prasad%2C%20a%20retailer%20on%20Park%20Street%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20says%20that%20introducing%20the%20Coca-Cola%20coolers%20has%20helped%20reshape%20his%20business%2C%20enabling%20him%20to%20stock%20up%20more%20products%2C%20all%20resulting%20in%20more%20sales.%20Lucknow%E2%80%99s%20Abhishek%20Pathak%20says%20beverage%20sales%20have%20soared%20since%20the%20installation%20of%20Coca-Cola%20India%20coolers%2C%20which%20keep%20the%20beverages%20refreshingly%20chilled%20and%20help%20attract%20more%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-5-1717573892.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Retail%20business%20owners%20with%20Coca-Cola%20coolers%20in%20their%20kirana%20stores%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-5-1717573892.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-5-1717573892-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2