ality%20and%20size%20of%20their%20mangoes.%20The%20transformation%20process%20started%20during%20his%20second%20year%20of%20college%20when%20he%20and%20his%20father%20decided%20to%20replace%20pesticides%20with%20Neem%20oil%20extract.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEncouraged%20by%20the%20results%2C%20Rohan%20branded%20their%20produce%20as%20%E2%80%9CSure%20Organics%E2%80%9D.%20Rohan%E2%80%99s%20farm%20grows%20various%20mango%20varieties%2C%20including%20%3Cem%3Edasheri%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Elangra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Echaunsa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Esafeda%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20along%20with%20lychee%20and%20turmeric.%20Over%20three%20years%2C%20his%20farm%20achieved%20organic%20certification%2C%20boosting%20their%20revenue%20significantly%20and%20increasing%20overall%20productivity%20by%2040%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E8.%20S%20Sivaganesh%E2%80%99s%20homecoming%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20as%20an%20engineer%20at%20an%20atomic%20station%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20S%20Sivaganesh%20always%20felt%20something%20was%20amiss.%20Growing%20up%20in%20nature%20with%20a%20farmer%20father%2C%20he%20longed%20to%20go%20back%20home%20and%20start%20farming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20for%20four%20years%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20move%20back%20to%20his%20hometown%20in%20Meenakshipuram%2C%20at%20the%20Kerala-Tamil%20Nadu%20border%2C%20in%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESivaganesh%20asked%20his%20father%20for%206%20acres%20of%20land%20to%20practise%20organic%20farming.%20%E2%80%9CI%20planted%20nutmegs%20as%20an%20intercrop%20along%20the%20coconut%20plantations%20of%201%2C600%2C%20and%20took%20up%20mango%2C%20turmeric%2C%20pepper%2C%20and%20areca%20nut%20plantations%20across%20my%206-acre%20farm%20along%20with%20it.%20I%20used%20organic%20methods%20for%20all%20the%20crops%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20started%20meaning%20Rs%202%20lakh%20per%20acre%20as%20a%20combined%20income%20from%20all%20plantations.%20His%